content.title: Netstrata welcome the owners of 268 Flood Street Leichhardt
content.author: S J
content.main_content:
Netstrata is proud to announce that they have been appointed by the owners corporation at 268 Flood Street, Leichhardt. The strata scheme comprises 38 townhouses set amongst well established botanical type gardens. The scheme will be managed by Christine Ashfield-Howell and she can be contacted direct on 02 8567 6420. Business Development Manager Jeremy Stone said “after going through an extensive tender and selection process it was fantastic to be appointed and we look forward to working with the committee in order to add some real value to this strata property, delivered through our proactive management approach”.
